{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they saw from the beginning that this was not the way that the country of Goethe and Beethoven and Schiller and Schopenhauer could end its history, with these-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] these horrendous extremes and brutalities and totally, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] totally inhuman actions.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My feelings were more skeptical.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also hoped that it would eventually come to an end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always knew, even at the time when Hitler was already at war with the United States and with half the world, that he would come down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it looked like he was winning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were many skeptical people, even in this country, who thought the Nazis are winning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're winning.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It looked like they're winning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always knew in my heart that they must lose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the reason why I emigrated and left Germany is that the general feeling of the older generation, like my parents, was get the kids out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They will leave us alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But for the young people, there is no future.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There is no way to make a living.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is no way to make a career.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they have to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that might also have been my reluctance to put them into a -- to put them into jeopardy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because by the time, I lived no longer in Fuerth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The family had moved to Munich because we believed, erroneously, that the bigger city and the more international city, the university-- large university city with many foreigners living there would be a safer place for us than Fuerth, where close to Nuremberg, which was the birthplace of Nazism and had this terrible Julius Streicher, who was the [INAUDIBLE] of Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[AUDIO OUT]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
